text.title: BINNENGEKOMEN.
text.p: TEXEL, 30 Dcc; Favourito. Robertson, Bahia, 1. v. Queenstow. - Albcrta 'Rocmeliug, de Vries, Grangcmouth. - Pascoc Crenfcll, Blaer, Sunderland... Beatitude, Halladay, id. VLIE, 28 Dcc; Geertruida Jacoba, Bontekoe, Gothenburg, is wegens ijsgang in de Sloot gezeild.
